      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "SLIDING 60-SEC WINDOW (now = 00:10)\nWindow spans: 00:10 - 01:00 (previous 60 sec)\nCount requests in this window\nLimit: 100 requests/minute\nIf count >= 100 → reject new request",
